<tr>
<td colspan="2">
<p>*Tuition is based on an annual amount, which is divided into 10 equal payments, You may pay the entire amount at the beginning of the year, or make monthly payments by the first of each month, August 1st through May 1st. If the first falls on a Saturday or Sunday, payments will be due the previous Friday. If payments are not made by the 10th of each month, a late fee will be charged to your account. Tuition may be dropped into the tuition payment box or mailed to HILLTOP Christian School, 5700 SW Dosch Rd, Portland, OR 97239</p>
<p>** After School Kids M-F will be billed on a per hour basis with $4.00/half hour charge when a child is late being picked up beyond a 5 minute grace period. Your balance due will be reflected on your monthly invoice from Hilltop.</p>
</td>
