<p><em>*Hilltop Preschool &amp; Kindergarten, a preschool in Portland, Oregon just off of Beaverton Hillsdale Hwy and Dosch Rd, is a ministry of Portland Christian Center and able to offer value-based fees that are less than other preschools. &nbsp;This allows us to offer excellent programs and services to support the busy family.</em></p>